They call it the Millennial Ache. We are the last generation that remembers life before the internet, before social media, before life became so loud and fast. We had a foot in both worlds—the analog and the digital. There is something so bittersweet about seeing these grainy videos and remembering how simple life was back then.  I’m making it my mission to bring these memories into the light before they’re gone for good. Thank you all for coming along for the ride! ❤️✨
